"    Execute the <span class=\"code\">nautilus</span> command to open the file\n"
"    browser with administration rights.\n"
"  </li>\n"
"  <li>\n"
"    In the file browser, navigate to <span class=\"filename\">\n"
"    /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked</span>.\n"
"  </li>\n"
"  <li>\n"
